Betadine Ointment is a topical antiseptic that is used to treat &amp; prevent infections in minor wounds or cuts. It provides infection protection against a variety of germs that can cause infection in minor cuts, wounds, scrapes and burns. It contains povidone-iodine as its active ingredient. A person with a known allergy to povidone-iodine should not use this medicine. Betadine Ointment is meant for external use and should be applied exactly as recommended by your doctor.','1','10:12 AM') , ('142','7744','BETADINE SOL(5% )500 ML *','BETADINESOL5500ML','500ML','08/25','MK0203','62.000','0','0','180.6','240.8','193.1698','19.78','166.15','721','77','WINTHROP','WINTHROP','WM','N','Y','','2011-06-30','0','12.00','','0','0','4.5','uploads/manage_medicine_image/photo/resize/Betadine_Sol_500.jpg','uploads/manage_medicine_image/photo/resize/Betadine_Sol_5001.jpg','uploads/manage_medicine_image/photo/resize/Betadine_Sol_5002.jpg','uploads/manage_medicine_image/photo/resize/Betadine_Sol_5003.jpg','SALT COMPOSITION
