endazole (400mg)','Bendex 400 Tablet is an antiparasitic medicine used for the treatment of parasitic worm infections It works by killing the worms that cause infections and stops the infection from spreading br br Bendex 400 Tablet should be used in the dose and duration as advised by your doctor Take it with or without food preferably at a fixed time Avoid skipping any doses and finish the full course of treatment even if you feel better Do not take a double dose to make up for a missed dose Simply take the next dose as planned br br Some people may experience vomiting dizziness increased liver enzymes nausea and loss of appetite as the side effects of this medicine Please consult your doctor if these side effects persist for a longer duration You may be monitored with blood tests and liver function tests throughout your treatment ','1','10:12 AM') , ('358','32006808','BENDEX SUSP.10ML *','BENDEXSUSP10ML','10ML','','','0.000','0','0','0','0','0','NaN','0','725','66','CIPLA LT','CIPLA LTD.','R26','N','Y','','2011-06-30','0','12.00','','0','0','4.5','','','','','Albendazole (200mg)','Bendex 200mg Suspension is an antiparasitic medicine used for the treatment of parasitic worm infections It works by killing the worms that cause infections and stops the infection from spreading br br Bendex 200mg Suspension should be used in the dose and duration as advised by your doctor Take it with or without food preferably at a fixed time Avoid skipping any doses and finish the full course of treatment even if you feel better Do not take a double dose to make up for a missed dose Simply take the next dose as planned br br Some people may experience vomiting dizziness increased liver enzymes nausea and loss of appetite as the side effects of this medicine Please consult your doctor if these side effects persist for a longer duration You may be monitored with blood tests and liver function tests throughout your treatment ','1','10:12 AM') , ('364','32006852','CEFADUR 500 TAB.','CEFADUR500TAB','10`S','','','0.000','0','0','0','0','0','NaN','0','725','66','CIPLA LT','CIPLA LTD.','R28','N','Y','','2011-06-30','0','12.00','','0','0','4.5','uploads/manage_medicine_image/photo/resize/CEFADUR_500_TAB.jpg','uploads/manage_medicine_image/photo/resize/CEFADUR_500_TAB1.jpg','','','','CEFADUR 500MG TABLET is an antibiotic. It is used to treat bacterial infections of the throat and upper part of the respiratory tract, skin and soft tissues, and the urinary tract.','1','10:12 AM') , ('366','32006888','CHESTON EXP.100ML','CHESTONEXP100ML','100ML','','','0.000','0','0','0','0','0','NaN','0','725','66','CIPLA LT','CIPLA LTD.','R28','N','Y','','2011-06-30','0','12.00','','0','0','4.5','uploads/manage_medicine_image/photo/resize/CHESTON_EXP.100ML.jpg','uploads/manage_medicine_image/photo/resize/CHESTON_EXP.100ML2.jpg','','','','CHESTON EXPECTORANT is a combination of Bromhexine, Chlorpheniramine maleate and Guaifenesin which belongs to the group of medicines called Mucolytics, Antihistamines and Nasal decongestants. It is used for symptomatic relief of productive cough.','1','10:12 AM') , ('371','32007597','RESTYL-0.25 TAB','RESTYL025TAB','15`S','06/26','SB30726','101.000','0','0','22.12','30.97','23.65955','23.60493','19.91','725','66','CIPLA LT','CIPLA LTD.','R26','N','Y','#NRX','2011-06-30','17977','12.00','','0','0','4.5','','','','','','','1','10:12 AM') , ('372','32007599','RESTYL-0.5 TAB *','RESTYL05TAB','15`S','07/26','SB30842','15.000','0','0','44.9','62.86','48.02504','23.6','40.41','725','66','CIPLA LT','CIPLA LTD.','R26','N','Y','#NRX','2011-06-30','17977','12.00','','0','0','4.5','','','','','','','1','10:12 AM') , ('379','32007223','IPRAVENT RESP.SOL.','IPRAVENTRESPSOL','15ML','12/24','SA30266','76.000','0','0','33.71','47.2','36.05622','23.60971','30.34','725','66','CIPLA LT','CIPLA LTD.','R15','N','Y','','2011-06-30','0','12.00','','0','0','4.5','','','','','','','1','10:12 AM') , ('380','0049','AMCARD - 2.5','AMCARD25','10`S','05/26','HAX030623','57.000','0','0','7.5','10.5','8.022','23.6','6.75','724','008','SYSTOPIC','SYSTOPIC','00','N','N','','2011-06-30','0','12.00','','0','0','4.5','','','','','','','1','10:12 AM') , ('382','0050','AMCARD - 5','AMCARD5','2X7`S','05/26','HAY100623','254.000','0','0','22.5','31.5','24.066','23.60001','20.25','724','008','SYSTOPIC','SYSTOPIC','00','N','Y','','2011-06-30','0','12.00','','0','0','4.5','','','','','','','1','10:12 AM') , ('383','0051','AMCARD-10','AMCARD10','10`S','04/26','HAT020523','40.000','0','0','27.14','38','29.02894','23.60805','24.43','724','008','SYSTOPIC','SYSTOPIC','00','N','N','','2011-06-30','0','12.00','','0','0','4.5','','','','','','','1','10:12 AM') , ('385','32006821','BUDECORT-100 INH. *','BUDECORT100INH','200MD','08/25','SN31614','153.000','0','0','252.8','353.92','270.3949','23.60001','227.52','725','66','CIPLA LT','CIPLA LTD.','R19','N','N','','2011-06-30','17810','12.00','','0','0','4.5','medicine_images/b_med/b_med0170.png','medicine_images/b_med/b_med1170.png','medicine_images/b_med/b_med2170.png','medicine_images/b_med/b_med3170.png','Budesonide (100mcg)','Budecort 100 Inhaler is used to prevent the symptoms of asthma wheezing and shortness of breath It is a steroid and is known as a preventer You need to have a fast acting reliever as well because this medicine will not stop an asthma attack that has already started br br Your doctor will tell you how often you need to use Budecort 100 Inhaler It is important that you take the lowest dose needed to effectively control your asthma The effect of this medicine may be noticeable after a few days but will only reach its maximum after a few weeks This medicine must be used regularly to be effective so go on taking it even if you do not have any symptoms No symptoms mean that the medicine is doing its job If you stop taking it your asthma may get worse It should not be used to relieve sudden asthma attacks If an asthma attack occurs use your quick relief inhaler reliever To get the benefit from this medicine you need to make sure you get your inhaler technique right otherwise it will not work as well br br The most common side effects are irritation in the throat difficulty swallowing and fungal infections in the mouth or throat If you get these do not stop taking it but do talk to your doctor You can help prevent these symptoms by rinsing your mouth and throat with water or brushing your teeth after using your inhaler There are other rare side effects that can be serious Talk to your doctor if you are worried about them In general you should be trying to avoid situations that make your asthma worse your triggers and try not to smoke br br Before taking Budecort 100 Inhaler you should tell your doctor if you have tuberculosis any infections in your mouth or lungs or liver disease While taking it you may be more at risk of getting infections so stay away from people with colds and flu If you use Budecort 100 Inhaler for a long time it may cause weak bones osteoporosis and damage to your eyes glaucoma or cataracts You might need tests for bone density and eye pressure Ask your doctor whether it s safe to take this medicine if you are pregnant or breastfeeding ','1','10:12 AM') , ('386','32007068','EMESET - 4  TABS.*','EMESET4TABS','10`S','06/26','SN31230','1626.000','5','1','41.04','57.45','43.89639','23.59202','36.93','725','66','CIPLA LT','CIPLA LTD.','R27','N','Y','','2011-06-30','0','12.00','','20','0','4.5','medicine_images/e_med/e_med015.png','medicine_images/e_med/e_med115.png','medicine_images/e_med/e_med215.png','medicine_images/e_med/e_med315.png','Ondansetron (4mg)','Emeset 4 Tablet is an antiemetic medicine commonly used to control nausea and vomiting due to certain medical conditions like stomach upset It is also used to prevent nausea and vomiting caused due to any surgery cancer drug therapy or radiotherapy br br Emeset 4 Tablet may be used alone or with other medications and can be taken with or without food Your doctor will suggest the appropriate dose depending on what you are taking it for The first dose is normally taken before the start of surgery chemotherapy or radiotherapy After these treatments take any further doses as prescribed by your doctor normally only for a few days at most Take it regularly at the same time s each day to get the most benefit Be careful not to take too much br br This medicine does not relieve other side effects associated with cancer treatments Also it has little effect on vomiting caused by motion sickness The most common side effects of taking this medicine include headache diarrhea or constipation and feeling tired These symptoms should disappear when you stop taking the medicine However if these side effects bother you or do not go away your doctor may be able to suggest ways of preventing or reducing them br br Before taking this medicine tell your doctor if you have heart or liver problems or a blockage in your stomach or intestines Also tell your doctor about any other medicines you might be taking especially medicines to treat epilepsy heart problems cancer and depression These may affect or be affected by this medicine If you are pregnant or breastfeeding ask for advice from your doctor ','1','10:12 AM') , ('387','32007069','EMESET  - 8  TABS *','EMESET8TABS','10`S','04/26','SN30711','449.000','5','1','72.4','101.36','77.43904','23.6','65.16','725','66','CIPLA LT','CIPLA LTD.','R27','N','Y','','2011-06-30','0','12.00','','20','0','4.5','medicine_images/e_med/e_med0225.png','medicine_images/e_med/e_med1225.png','medicine_images/e_med/e_med2225.png','medicine_images/e_med/e_med3225.png','Ondansetron (8mg)','Emeset 8 Tablet is an antiemetic medicine commonly used to control nausea and vomiting due to certain medical conditions like stomach upset It is also used to prevent nausea and vomiting caused due to any surgery cancer drug therapy or radiotherapy br br Emeset 8 Tablet may be used alone or with other medications and can be taken with or without food Your doctor will suggest the appropriate dose depending on what you are taking it for The first dose is normally taken before the start of surgery chemotherapy or radiotherapy After these treatments take any further doses as prescribed by your doctor normally only for a few days at most Take it regularly at the same time s each day to get the most benefit Be careful not to take too much br br This medicine does not relieve other side effects associated with cancer treatments Also it has little effect on vomiting caused by motion sickness The most common side effects of taking this medicine include headache diarrhea or constipation and feeling tired These symptoms should disappear when you stop taking the medicine However if these side effects bother you or do not go away your doctor may be able to suggest ways of preventing or reducing them br br Before taking this medicine tell your doctor if you have heart or liver problems or a blockage in your stomach or intestines Also tell your doctor about any other medicines you might be taking especially medicines to treat epilepsy heart problems cancer and depression These may affect or be affected by this medicine If you are pregnant or breastfeeding ask for advice from your doctor ','1','10:12 AM') , ('388','32007071','EMESET INJ.2ML#*','EMESETINJ2ML','2ML','06/26','S630077','4549.000','0','0','5.36','13.35','5.733056','57.05576','4.74','725','66','CIPLA LT','CIPLA LTD.','R27','N','N','','2011-06-30','0','12.00','','0','0','4.5','uploads/manage_medicine_image/photo/resize/Emeset_Inj.2ml.jpg','uploads/manage_medicine_image/photo/resize/Emeset_Inj.2ml.jpg','uploads/manage_medicine_image/photo/resize/Emeset_Inj.2ml.jpg','uploads/manage_medicine_image/photo/resize/Emeset_Inj.2ml.jpg','','ONDANSETRON-2MG/ML','1','10:12 AM') , ('389','32007072','EMESET INJ.4ML#*','EMESETINJ4ML','4ML','05/26','A030298','1285.000','0','0','11.48','26.7','12.27901','54.01121','10.28','725','66','CIPLA LT','CIPLA LTD.','R27','N','N','','2011-06-30','0','12.00','','0','0','4.5','','','','','Ondansetron (4mg)','Emeset Injection 2ml is an antiemetic medicine commonly used to control nausea and vomiting due to certain medical conditions like stomach upset It is also used to prevent nausea and vomiting caused due to any surgery cancer drug therapy or radiotherapy br br Emeset Injection 2ml will not relieve other side effects associated with cancer treatments It is given under the supervision of a doctor and may be used alone or with other medications Your doctor will give you appropriate dose depending on what you are taking it for It is important that you keep having the injections until your doctor decides it is safe to stop them After this your doctor may prescribe tablets instead of the injections br br The most common side effects of taking this medicine include injection site pain headache and constipation These symptoms should disappear when you stop taking the medicine But if these side effects bother you or do not go away consult your doctor who may be able to suggest ways of preventing or reducing them br br Before taking this medicine tell your doctor if you have heart or liver problems or a blockage in your stomach or intestines Also tell your doctor about other drugs you are using especially medicines to treat epilepsy heart problems cancer and depression These may affect or be affected by this medicine If you are pregnant or breastfeeding ask for advice from your healthcare team ','1','10:12 AM') , ('390','32007645','SEROBID INHALER','SEROBIDINHALER','120MD','','','0.000','0','0','0','0','0','NaN','0','725','66','CIPLA LT','CIPLA LTD.','R17','N','N','','2011-06-30','0','12.00','','0','0','4.5','','','','','','','1','10:12 AM') , ('391','32007646','SEROBID ROTOCAPS','SEROBIDROTOCAPS','30`S','','','0.000','0','0','0','0','0','NaN','0','725','66','CIPLA LT','CIPLA LTD.','R17','N','N','','2011-06-30','0','12.00','','0','0','4.5','','','','','','','1','10:12 AM') , ('392','32006751','ASTHALIN RESPULES',