ps throat or face swallowing or breathing problems feeling dizzy or faint and nausea Get emergency help if this happens Avoid direct contact with your eyes In case of direct contact wash your eyes with water and seek immediate medical attention br br It is not likely that other medicines you take by mouth or injection will affect the way this medicine works but talk to your doctor before using it if you have recently used another medicine that contains a steroid or had an allergic reaction to another antifungal medicine This medicine should only be used if it is clearly needed if you are pregnant or breastfeeding Ask your doctor if it is safe ','0','01:24 PM') , ('99','3320','IMOSEC  - M TAB.','IMOSECMTAB','4`S','','','0.000','0','0','0','0','0','NaN','0','717','33','ETHNOR','JANSSEN DIVISION J & J','JU','N','Y','','2011-06-30','0','12.00','','0','0','4.5','','','','','','','1','01:24 PM') , ('102','3327','NIZRAL TABS.','NIZRALTABS','10`S','','','0.000','0','0','0','0','0','NaN','0','717','33','ETHNOR','JANSSEN DIVISION J & J','OT','N','N','','2011-06-30','0','12.00','','0','0','4.5','','','','','','','1','01:24 PM') , ('106','3330','NIZRAL SHAMPOO','NIZRALSHAMPOO','50ML','10/25','3DW13','318.000','0','0','242.86','340','259.7631','23.5991','218.57','8559','230','A.MENRIN','A.MENRINI INDIA PVT LTD','00','N','Y','','2011-06-30','0','12.00','','0','0','4.5','uploads/manage_medicine_image/photo/resize/nizral.jpg','uploads/manage_medicine_image/photo/resize/nizral.jpg','uploads/manage_medicine_image/photo/resize/nizral.jpg','uploads/manage_medicine_image/photo/resize/nizral.jpg','','Composition: Ketoconazole IP 2 % ','1','01:24 PM') , ('108','3333','STUGERON  -  25 TAB','STUGERON25TAB','25`S','07/26','J21034','331.000','0','0','169.64','237.5','181.4469','23.60129','152.68','717','33','ETHNOR','JANSSEN DIVISION J & J','JU','N','N','','2011-06-30','0','12.00','','0','0','4.5','','','','','','','1','01:24 PM') , ('109','3334','STUGERON FORTE TAB','STUGERONFORTETAB','20`S'