passages, thus widening it and making it easier to breathe.

Theo-Asthalin Tablet is taken without food in a dose and duration as advised by the doctor. The dose you are given will depend on your condition and how you respond to the medicine. You should keep taking this medicine for as long as your doctor recommends. If you stop treatment too early your symptoms may come back and your condition may worsen. Let your healthcare team know about all other medications you are taking as some may affect, or be affected by this medicine.
','1','07:09 PM') , ('312','32007112','FELOGARD - 5','FELOGARD5','10`S','','','0.000','0','0','0','0','0','NaN','0','725','66','CIPLA LT','CIPLA LTD.','R29','N','N','','2011-06-30','0','12.00','','0','0','4.5','','','','','','','1','07:09 PM') , ('314','32006803','BECLATE-200 R/C','BECLATE200RC','30`S','11/25','BA23462','6.000','0','0','92.02','128.83','98.42459','23.60119','82.82','725','66','CIPLA LT','CIPLA LTD.','R17','N','N','','2011-06-30','0','12.00','','0','0','4.5','uploads/manage_medicine_image/photo/resize/BECLATE-200_Rc.jpg','uploads/manage_medicine_image/photo/resize/BECLATE-200_RC_2.jpg','','','Beclomethasone Dipropionate IP 200 mcg','Composition: Each capsule contains Beclomethasone Dipropionate IP 200 mcg. Excipients q.s','1','07:09 PM') , ('316','32006706','.AEROCORT ROTACAPS','.AEROCORTROTACAPS','30`S','','','0.000','0','0','0','0','0','NaN','0','725','66','CIPLA LT','CIPLA LTD.','R15','N','N','','2011-06-30','0','12.00','','0','0','4.5','medicine_images/a_med/a_med0209.png','medicine_images/a_med/a_med1209.png','medicine_images/a_med/a_med2209.png','medicine_images/a_med/a_med3209.png','Levosalbutamol (100mcg) + Beclometasone (100mcg)','Aerocort Rotacap is used in the treatment of asthma wheezing and shortness of breath It relaxes the muscles of the air passages and makes it easier to breathe br br Your doctor will tell you how often you need to use your inhaler It s important that you take the lowest dose needed to effectively control your asthma The effect of this medicine may be noticeable after a few days but will only reach its maximum after a few weeks This medicine must be used regularly to be effective so go on taking it even if you don t have any symptoms That means it s doing its job If you stop taking it your asthma may get worse It should not be used to relieve sudden asthma attacks If an asthma attack occurs use your quick relief inhaler reliever To get the benefit from this medicine you need to make sure you get your inhaler technique right otherwise it does not work as well br br The most common side effects are hoarseness of voice sore throat fungal infection of mouth respiratory tract infection headache and muscle cramp If you get these don t stop taking it but do talk to your doctor You can help prevent some of these symptoms by rinsing your mouth and throat with water or brushing your teeth after using your inhaler There are other rarer side effects which can be serious Talk to your doctor if you re worried about them In general you should be trying to avoid situations that make your asthma worse your triggers and try not to smoke br br Ask your doctor whether it s safe to take this medicine if you re pregnant or breastfeeding Before taking it you should tell your doctor if you have any kidney or liver diseases so that your doctor can prescribe a suitable dose for you ','0','07:09 PM') , ('318','10927','CLISTIN  DRY SYP.','CLISTINDRYSYP','100ML','','','0.000','0','0','0','0','0','NaN','0','8519','65','ERIS','ERIS LIFE SCIENCES','ER2','N','Y','','2011-06-30','0','12.00','','0','0','4.5','','','','','','','1','07:09 PM') , ('319','32014280','NEW THEO ASTHALIN SYP.','NEWTHEOASTHALINSYP','100ML','','','0.000','0','0','0','0','0','NaN','0','725','66','CIPLA LT','CIPLA LTD.','R26','N','Y','','2011-06-30','0','12.00','','0','0','4.5','','','','','','','1','07:09 PM') , ('324','0043','KINETO FORTE TABS','KINETOFORTETABS','10`S','04/25','KF032','285.000','0','0','54.29','76','58.06858','23.59397','48.86','724','008','SYSTOPIC','SYSTOPIC','00','N','Y','','2011-06-30','0','12.00','','0','0','4.5','','','','','','','1','07:09 PM') , ('325','32005992','OMNIX CV TAB','OMNIXCVTAB','10`S','03/24','ONX221007','30.000','5','1','219.1','306.74','234.3494','23.6','197.19','725','66','CIPLA LT','CIPLA LTD.','R26','N','Y','','2011-06-30','0','12.00','','20','0','4.5','','','','','','','1','07:09 PM') , ('326','32008924','NORFLOX - 100 DT','NORFLOX100DT','10`S','','','0.000','0','0','0','0','0','NaN','0','725','